  "2026-07-18T05:45:21.231Z",maintainer-agent,"Class broadened 2026-07-18: this item now owns ALL CodeFactor \"unnecessary spread\" findings (GH-553 test-side history read assertion + NEW GH-584 sdk/graph/run.ts:684). The GH-584 site is the exactOptionalPropertyTypes conditional-spread idiom `...(x === undefined ? {} : { kinds: x })` in runGraphCommunities — fix by building the options object without spread (explicit conditional assignment or a small buildOptions helper), preserving exact-optional typing. Sweep the graph run.ts family for sibling instances of the same idiom at fix time. Never file per-site spread point patches — extend this item."
